    "name": "HybridTreasury-MultiContract-RiskFactors-V2-6mo",
    "description": "ACTUS Hybrid Treasury: MULTI-CONTRACT PORTFOLIO with ENRICHED RISK FACTORS\n\n== V2 IMPROVEMENT ==\nReference indexes now model MARKET RISK FACTORS (observables),\nnot pre-computed schedules.\n\nMARKET RISK FACTORS (8 new + 3 legacy kept):\n  1. BTC_USD_SPOT      — BTC spot price (existing, correct)\n  2. UST_3M_YIELD      — 3-month US Treasury yield (Fed rate path)\n  3. USDC_USD_PEG       — USDC/USD peg rate (stablecoin depegging risk)\n  4. USDT_USD_PEG       — USDT/USD peg rate (alt stablecoin comparison)\n  5. BTC_REALIZED_VOL   — 30-day BTC realized volatility\n  6. DEFI_USDC_LEND_RATE— On-chain USDC lending APY (Aave/Compound)\n  7. ETH_STAKING_YIELD  — ETH staking APY (DeFi yield benchmark)\n  8. BTC_MVRV_RATIO     — Market Value / Realized Value (on-chain valuation)\n  9. PORTFOLIO_TOTAL_VALUE (legacy, kept for backward compatibility)\n 10. PROJECTED_OUTFLOWS    (legacy, kept for backward compatibility)\n 11. TBILL_MATURITY_SCHEDULE (legacy, kept for backward compatibility)\n\nBEHAVIORAL RISK FACTORS (5 models: 2 existing + 3 new):\n  1. ad_btc01  — AllocationDriftModel     (BTC allocation vs 20% target)\n  2. lb_tr01   — LiquidityBufferModel     (fiat buffer vs $3M minimum)\n  3. ps_usdc01 — PegStressModel           (USDC depeg risk monitoring)\n  4. ya_tr01   — YieldArbitrageModel      (TradFi vs DeFi yield spread)\n  5. fv_btc01  — FairValueComplianceModel (BTC fair value / MVRV overheating)\n\nCONTRACTS (7 ACTUS contracts):\n  1. STK  BTC-Position-40      40 BTC ($2M @ $50K)\n  2. PAM  TBILL-3mo-500K-Mar   $500K zero-coupon, matures Mar 31\n  3. PAM  TBILL-5mo-500K-May   $500K zero-coupon, matures May 31\n  4. PAM  TBILL-4mo-250K-Jun   $250K zero-coupon, matures Jun 30\n  5. PAM  TBILL-5mo-500K-Jul   $500K zero-coupon, matures Jul 31\n  6. PAM  USDC-Reserve-3M      $3M USDC reserve (stablecoin position)\n  7. PAM  FiatCash-5M          $5M fiat operating cash\n\nSCENARIO (6 months, Mar-Aug 2026):\n  BTC: $50K → $90K peak (Jun) → $65K (Aug)\n  Fed: easing cycle, 3M yield 4.25% → 3.75%\n  USDC peg: stable, minor stress 0.9985 during June turmoil\n  BTC vol: 45% → 85% spike → 55% cooldown\n  DeFi yields: rise 8% → 15% during crypto bull → 10% cooldown\n  MVRV: 2.1 (fair) → 3.8 (overheated) → 2.5 (correction)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
